INSERT INTO `couch_data_text` VALUES("13", "39", "<h2>\r\n	Family Support &amp; Prevention Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n	With the presense of the Family Center atop the West Hill, RAYS seeks to support the growth and development of families and all their members - adults, youth, and children alike - to build healthier families and ultimately a stronger community. Staff and families work together in relationships based on mutual equality and respect, while programs are flexible and continually responsive to emerging issues.</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n	Our programs &amp; services</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	The West Hill community recognizes the RAYS Family Center as a community space where they can go for a multitude of programs and services, or simply as a place to get out of the cold. More specifically the Family Center is home to or offers:</p>\r\n", "Family Support &amp; Prevention Services With the presense of the Family Center atop the West Hill, RAYS seeks to support the growth and development of families and all their members - adults, youth, and children alike - to build healthier families and ultimately a stronger community. Staff and families work together in relationships based on mutual equality and respect, while programs are flexible and continually responsive to emerging issues. Our programs &amp; services The West Hill community recognizes the RAYS Family Center as a community space where they can go for a multitude of programs and services, or simply as a place to get out of the cold. More specifically the Family Center is home to or offers:");
