n					Islands best no-bank beach, the cottage is just steps away\r\n					from breathtaking views of Mount Rainier, Rich Passage and\r\n					Blake Island. The yard is professionally landscaped and the\r\n					beach is accessed by a garden path.\r\n\r\n				</p>\r\n\r\n				<p>\r\n\r\n					Amenities include a queen size bed and four twin bunks, a\r\n					full bath, washer and dryer, fluffy terry robes and fresh\r\n					linens. There is an abundance of materials for reading,\r\n					writing, sketching, stargazing and dreaming. The cottage\r\n					is set in a secluded garden and shares 180 feet of\r\n					waterfront. Its a birders paradise, with kingfishers,\r\n					redwing blackbirds, eagles, osprey, blue herons, pipers,\r\n					swallows and songbirds. You might encounter otters, sea\r\n					lions and even the occasional orca pod.\r\n\r\n				</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n			", "Home", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "4-revision-v1", "", "", "2013-08-23 20:31:34", "2013-08-23 20:31:34", "", "4", "http://localhost/pw-house/wordpress/?p=5", "0", "revision", "", "0");
